 "<p>The reading activity, as the name\nsuggests, should ask the learner to perform some form of activity. This activity\nshould be directly related to the text the learner has been asked to read.\nFeedback to the activity where appropriate, can provide the learner with some\nreflective guidance.<\/p>": "<p>L'activit\u00e9 de lecture, comme son nom indique, \nexige \u00e0 l'\u00e9tudiant la r\u00e9alisation d'une activit\u00e9 concr\u00e8te. Cette activit\u00e9 \ndevra \u00eatre directement li\u00e9e au texte que l'\u00e9tudiant a d\u00fb lire. \nCertains commentaires sur l'activit\u00e9, situ\u00e9s aux endroits strat\u00e9giques, peuvent permettre \u00e0 l'\u00e9tudiant une\nr\u00e9flexion guid\u00e9e.<\/p>", 
